;; Shortcuts for windows management
;;
;; | Shortcut          | Summary                         |
;; | ----------------- | ------------------------------- |
;; | Right Alt + Esc   | Close window (Alt + F4)         |
;; | Right Alt + +     | Maximise window                 |
;; | Right Alt + -     | Minimise window                 |
;; | Right Alt + `     | Move window between monitors    |
;; | ----------------- | ------------------------------- |


